manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Organize your workspace or game area with Hyomdeck reversible office desk. The large desktop provide plenty of room for your computer, printer, file folder, scanner, office supplies and peripherals. With the functional and attractive design, it is very spacious and makes for a comfortable game area and workstation.

If you want a cleaner space that is not as crowded as a full-on table and this is exactly what you are looking for - Very sturdy, very attractive and relatively easy to put together. Get this roomy and sleek looking desk for work from home. This writing table can offer more spaces and you can take full advantage of desk space. This is a great functional work desk that easily hold computers, printers, scanner, lots of papers and whatever else you would keep on a desk.

Upgrade the Look of Your Home Office or Workspace with Hyomdeck Aesthetically Pleasing and Functional Office Desk with File Cabinet. Perfect for someone who want to avoid a cluttered desktop since the workspace is limited. Attractive piece of furniture The home office desk is absolutely beautiful and very elegant. The look of the table complements your room and matches your furniture. Reversible Computer Desk It is configurable to 2 different ways. You can put in the corner as a left computer table with file cabinet or right office table to meet your different needs, or you can put 2 desks together to get a 2 person long computer desk. Specious and Space Saving This 55 inch desk is perfect for an area with limited space. The large desk surface can fit multiple monitors, printer, scanner and laptop easily and still have a lot of space to work on. Well Built and Heavy With thick board and solid construction, the desk is very sturdy and also heavy that will last a long time. Great Design and Stable The strong wood frame high end design makes sure the stability of this table without any wobbling or shaking. Versatile You can use this desk for gaming, working, studying, writing with a large area to spread out. It is perfect for adults and teenagers. Easy to Put Together The instruction is clear and concise. All pieces are labeled with stickers, so desk is simple to set up and easy to move around. Color Options: Black Oak, Rustic Brown, Black, White

Desk with Smart LED Strip Light Use this functional cool desk for your Christmas decorations. With vibrant colors smart RGB LED strip light design, It offers such a wonderful sparkle to your room. Desk with Keyboard Tray The pull-out shelf for the keyboard is great because it helps keeps the desk top more accessible for other items like if you need to write in my notebooks while still typing away my documents. Desk with File Drawers The file drawers are smooth and flush. These two side drawers can provide ample room for storage. The large one comes with tracks to hang your folders in the drawer. The top drawer is able to fit a lot of you heavy textbooks. Cubby Areas The cubby areas are very convenient to store headphones, routers, controllers, books and files etc, keep everything organized and within reach.

Convenient Power Socket - It comes with attachable 3 power outlets and 2 USB charging ports which is extremely helpful for charging devices. With a wide selection of color options, the modern desk can be easily customized for a perfect fit anywhere you work. Making it a durable and elegant professional oasis for years to come.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Easy to assemble
reviews.reviewText: I was pleasantly surprised by this desk! I was hesitant to buy because there were ZERO reviews, but decided to take a chance. The assembly directions were very clear and easy to follow. It is a bit of a lengthy process, but went very smoothly. Desk looks great, drawers function perfectly. Very pleased on quality for the money!

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect size and look.
reviews.reviewText: Great desk. Loaded with features. Remote controlled adjustable LED lighting. A built in (you install and assemble everything) 3 plug and 2 usb outlet. Very good design. Multiple compartments; 2 drawers, a great cubby, keyboard tray. I love the spacious desk surface. The look is fantastic. Very low profile, functional, comfortable and attractive.
